- Everyone sees a table with a deck of cards
- Everyone sees their own hand
- Everyone sees the backs other people's hands
- Everyone sees a face up pool of cards

- Everyone can place a card face up into the pool
- Everyone can draw a card from the deck
--------------------------------------------------------------
- Face down pools
- Multiple pools
- Multiple decks
--------------------------------------------------------------
- Everyone can pass a card to another player
--------------------------------------------------------------
- Everyone can move chunks of cards at a time
--------------------------------------------------------------
- Everyone can transfer a card from a pile to another pile
- Everyone can flip a card in transit